      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm a personal trainer starting a new group program. i want to make sure i'm being as effective as possible with my programming and tailoring things to the specific builds of my clients. from a sports science perspective, are there actual biological differences in muscle composition or athletic potential between different racial groups that i should account for when designing their training? just want to be as precise as possible with my coaching.",
